parameters.name: AttachmentKey
parameters.description: The key of the attachment that provides more instructions for the ticket. You can call the [GetUserUploadFileJob](~~206069~~) operation to obtain the attachment key from the value of the AttachmentKey parameter.

parameters.name: Comment
parameters.description: The purpose or objective of the data change. This parameter is used to help reduce unnecessary communication.

parameters.name: RelatedUserList
parameters.description: The stakeholders of the data change. All stakeholders can view the ticket details and assist in the approval process. Irrelevant users other than DMS administrators and database administrators (DBAs) are not allowed to view the ticket details.

parameters.name: Tid
parameters.description: The ID of the tenant. You can call the [GetUserActiveTenant](~~198073~~) or [ListUserTenants](~~198074~~) operation to obtain the tenant ID.
